en.%20She's%20been%20Altman's%20right-hand%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glaring%20void%20in%20OpenAI's%20C-suite%20has%20become%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-talent-exodus-joke-tech-world-mira-murati-sam-altman-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20joke%20of%20the%20moment%20among%20VCs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%2C%20as%20far%20as%20he's%20concerned%2C%20%26quot%3Bleadership%20changes%20are%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20companies%2C%20especially%20companies%20that%20grow%20so%20quickly%20and%20are%20so%20demanding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20obviously%20won't%20pretend%20it's%20natural%20for%20this%20one%20to%20be%20so%20abrupt%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20a%20normal%20company%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20reasons%20Mira%20explained%20to%20me%20(there%20is%20never%20a%20good%20time%2C%20anything%20not%20abrupt%20would%20have%20leaked%2C%20and%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%20this%20while%20OpenAI%20was%20in%20an%20upswing)%20make%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F1839096160168063488%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283436fe9-c75a-4529-9904-642bc9c41852%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpenAI's%20conversion%20to%20a%20for-profit%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20big%20Musk%20lawsuit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Murati's%20announcement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fopenai-remove-non-profit-control-give-sam-altman-equity-sources-say-2024-09-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-sam-altman-equity-stake-valuation-private-nonprofit-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enonprofit%20board%20will%20no%20longer%20control%20the%20company's%20for-profit%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20anonymous%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nonprofit%20side%20of%20OpenAI%20will%20still%20exist%20and%20have%20a%20minority%20stake%20in%20the%20for-profit%20company%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20change%20to%20a%20for-profit%20governance%20structure%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20Park%2C%20the%20corporate%20law%20expert%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20ambitions%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20a%20non-profit%20structure%20has%20been%20too%20constraining.%20To%20raise%20investor%20funds%2C%20OpenAI%20will%20have%20to%20generate%20profits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20whether%20OpenAI%20should%20be%20a%20for-profit%20company%20has%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20for%20one%20very%20vocal%20tech%20industry%20bigwig%20%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20one%20of%20the%20cofounders%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sues-openai-sam-altman-again-why-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevived%20his%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musk%20is%20now%20accusing%20OpenAI%20of%20deceiving%20him%20into%20co-founding%20the%20firm.%20Musk's%20lawyers%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20Altman%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20con%26quot%3B%20to%20convince%20Musk%20that%20OpenAI%20would%20be%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20would%20build%20a%20safe%20AI%20to%20benefit%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Musk's%20renewed%20legal%20battle%20against%20it%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-fightingwars-alot-of-fronts-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20August%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20said%20about%20Elon's%20initial%20legal%20filing%2C%20which%20was%20subsequently%20w