ofit%20board%2C%20and%20Altman%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20would%20receive%20equity%2C%20sources%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20jettisoning%20any%20layer%20of%20oversight%20that%20might%20make%20them%20responsible%20to%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcus%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BHow%20could%20that%20not%20be%20worrying%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPark%2C%20the%20corporate%20law%20expert%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20for-profit%20governance%20structure%20could%20also%20leave%20OpenAI%20vulnerable%20to%20greater%20government%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20danger%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20stronger%20argument%20for%20government%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20company's%20efforts%20because%20of%20the%20concern%20it%20will%20take%20unacceptable%20risks%20in%20pursuing%20profitability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ed2325d-aea5-4e1a-beb2-8f70e366415d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20growing%20field%20of%20competition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20company%20hopes%20to%20attract%20and%20retain%20top%20talent%2C%20OpenAI%20also%20faces%20several%20formidable%20competitors%2C%20including%20Meta%20and%20Musk's%20xAI%2C%20which%20just%20got%20a%20new%20supercomputer%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20launched%20its%20latest%20iteration%20of%20its%20language%20model%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-open-source-ai-platforms-future-competition-apple-llama-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELlama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20July.%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-llama-ai-model-praise-open-source-musk-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-source%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20xAI%20is%20also%20starting%20to%20play%20catch-up%20with%20rivals%20after%20the%20company%20debuted%20its%20supercomputer%2C%20