age%20employee%20in%20India%20worked%2046.7%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20compared%20to%20about%2038%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20are%20employees%20in%20India%20working%20long%20hours%2C%20but%20many%20are%20also%20doing%20it%20under%20intense%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pressure%20is%20very%2C%20very%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Jennifer%20Hephzibah%2C%20a%20senior%20HR%20professional%20in%20India%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20deliver%20it%20at%20a%20particular%20time%2C%20you%20either%20lose%20your%20bonus%2C%20or%20you%20lose%20your%20job.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20you're%20going%20through%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcg.com%2Fpublications%2F2024%2Findia-hr-revolution-building-workplaces-for-the-future%26sa%3DD%26source%3Ddocs%26ust%3D1727195342438866%26usg%3DAOvVaw366N6_QMHZIy6fbfnMv__Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2011%2C000%20workers%20in%20eight%20countries%20in%20October%202023%20found%20that%2058%25%20of%20Indian%20respondents%20reported%20feeling%20burned%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20share%20of%20any%20of%20the%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%20(50%25)%2C%20the%20UK%20(47%25)%2C%20and%20Japan%20(37%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256dd16d5-8f41-4ab5-aad1-efb517f1a780%5C%22%3E'Glorifying%20overwork'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20always-on%20culture%20has%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%20recently%20following%20the%20death%20of%20an%20EY%20employee%2C%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeryail's%20father%2C%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fwhat-action-will-ey-take-anna-sebastians-father-speaks-to-tnm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20believed%20his%20daughter%20died%20of%20a%20combination%20of%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20work%20stress%20and%20acid%20reflux%20which%20triggered%20a%20lack%20of%20sleep.%20The%20official%20cause%20of%20Perayil's%20death%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnna%20was%20unable%20to%20sleep%20on%20most%20days%20and%20couldn't%20eat%20on%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20publication.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20whole%20night%20of%20work%2C%20she%20would%20have%20to%20wake%20up%20at%207%3A30%20the%20next%20morning%20and%20repeat%20the%20same%20cycle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmaharashtra%2Fmother-pens-letter-following-death-of-26-year-old-daughter-due-to-work-stress-urges-ey-chairman-to-reflect-on-toxic-work-culture%2Farticle68656957.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Perayil's%20mother%20emailed%20Rajiv%20Memani%2C%20the%20chairman%20at%20EY%20India%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Perayil's%20death%2C%20saying%20her%20daughter%20had%20collapsed%20four%20months%20into%20the%20job%20after%20struggling%20with%20%26quot%3Bthe%20workload%2C%20new%20environment%2C%20and%20long%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20accused%20EY%20of%20%26quot%3Bglorifying%20overwork.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEY%20told%20BI%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btaking%20the%20family's%20correspondence%20with%20utmost%20seriousness%20and%20humility%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20Perayil's%20death%20an%20%26quot%3Birreparable%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e580f7b-a1b5-40de-bcd5-4c5e1cd9f1da%5C%22%3EA%2070-hour%20workweek%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20India's%20workplace%20culture%20are%20not%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20software%20billionaire%20and%20Infosys%20founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%20sparked%20controversy%20after%20saying%20that%20young%20people%20in%20India%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week%20to%20help%20the%20country%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DES8ZNSTswrs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Record%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20going%20on%20to%20say%20that%20unless%20India%20improved%20several%20factors%20including%20its%20work%20productivity%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20those%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20tremendous%20progress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20therefore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20request%20is%20that%20our%20youngsters%20must%20say%3A%20%26quot%3B'This%20is%20my%20country.%20I'd%20like%20to%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20appear%20to%20reflect%20wider%20expectations%20in%20India%2C%20even%20among%20employers%20with%20head%20offices%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKavach%20Khanna%2C%20a%20former%20EY%20analyst%20in%20India%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20believed%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20do%20more%20work%20than%20his%20US%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20colleagues%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%20same%20roles%2C%20and%20their%20experience%20was%20completely%20different%20from%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Khanna%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20get%20to%20go%20for%20client%20meetings%2C%20leave%20the%20office%20on%20time%2C%20no%20stretched%20workdays%2C%20and%20they%20weren't%20overburdened%20like%20we%20were.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEY%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c34411b0-4cf7-4ac6-b8b5-d828d78369df%5C%22%3ECost%20centers%20and%20cheap%20labor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuge%20multinational%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20EY%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Salesforce%2C%20and%20Accenture%2C%20have%20set%20up%20cost%20centers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20centers%2C%20also%20called%20Global%20Capability%20Centers%20(GCCs)%2C%20manage%20everything%20from%20cyber%20security%20to%20product%20development.%20They%20can%20also%20manage%20human%20resources%20and%20accounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20cheaper%20to%20run%20in%20India%20due%20to%20lower%20labor%20costs%2C%20and%20they%20help%20companies%20tap%20into%20a%20wide%20and%20hungry%20pool%20of%20tech-savvy%2C%20English-speaking%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.ey.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fey-sites%2Fey-com%2Fen_in%2Ftopics%2Fconsulting%2Fgcc%2F2023%2F06%2Fey-future-of-gccs-in-india-a-vision-2030.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEY%20report%20in%202023%20%3C%2Fa%3Eprojected%20that%20India%20is%20set%20to%20host%20at%20least%202%2C400%20such%20centers%20by%202030%2C%20with%20a%20market%20value%20of%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20associate%20at%20the%20Indian%20office%20of%20a%20multinational%20banking%20and%20advisory%20firm%20told%20BI%20that%20even%20at%20his%20Western%20company%2C%20he%20believed%20Indian%20employees%20were%20expected%20to%20work%20longer%20and%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2016-%20to%2018-hour%20workdays%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20weekends%20%E2%80%94%20were%20normal%20in%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20multinational%20corporations%20use%20India%20as%20a%20cost%20center%20because%20of%20the%20cheap%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20associate%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation.%20%26quot%3BOffices%20in%20other%20countries%20have%20boundaries%20and%20then%20dump%20their%20extra%20work%20on%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeanie%20Chang%2C%20an%20executive%20coach%20who%20specializes%20in%20workplace%20mental%20health%2C%20said%20she%20had%20noticed%20such%20a%20trend%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20exists%20that%20multinational%20companies%20tend%20to%20think%2C%20'We%20love%20that%20the%20Indians%20work%20hard%2C%20so%20let's%20keep%20doing%20that.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20also%20noted%20that%20some%20Asian%20communities%20place%20a%20cultural%20importance%20on%20work%20ethic%20that%20can%20lend%20itself%20to%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20word%20in%20Japanese%20and%20Korean%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20literally%20means%20'overworking%20yourself%20to%20death.'%20That%20should%20say%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22799c5726-4028-4993-85d3-1175f4f96f4d%5C%22%3EFear%20of%20replacement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20stopping%20employees%20from%20demanding%20change%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20it%20might%20come%20down%20to%20competition.%20In%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaenvironmentportal.org.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2FIndia%2520Employment%2520Report%25202024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20India%20Employment%20Report%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India's%20youth%20made%20up%20nearly%2083%25%20of%20the%20country's%20total%20unemployed%20population.%20With%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2F68432023-Economic-Survey-2023-24-Complete-document%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia's%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20thought%20to%20number%20well%20over%20500%20million%2C%20each%20job%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHephzibah%2C%20the%20senior%20HR%20professional%2C%20said%20that%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20available%20workers%20has%20contributed%20to%20a%20feeling%20that%20employees%20are%20expendable%2C%20and%20has%20held%20them%20back%20from%20saying%20no%20to%20unreasonable%20demands%20for%20fear%20of%20losing%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerayil's%20mother's%20email%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20said%20her%20daughter%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20know%20how%20to%20say%20no.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20trying%20to%20prove%20herself%20in%20a%20new%20environment%2C%20and%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20she%20pushed%20herself%20beyond%20her%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHephzibah%20said%20this%20was%20especially%20true%20for%20younger%20workers%2C%20who%20may%20not%20have%20enough%20experience%20to%20become%20critical%20within%20the%20company%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20bigger%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20don't%20deliver%2C%20that's%20it%3A%20You're%20replaced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276d9e66d-7e50-4929-bb3f-86da08d669dd%5C%22%3ECultural%20differences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20told%20BI%20that%20she's%20had%20Indian%20employees%20point%20out%20their%20lack%20of%20resources%20compared%20to%20international%20peers%20in%20the%20same%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tell%20me%2C%20'Jeanie%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20effective%20mental-health%20resources%2C%20but%20we%20hear%20the%20US%20does%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F349484%2Fstate-of-the-global-workplace.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Gallup%20State%20of%20the%20Global%20Workplace%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202024%2C%20only%2014%25%20of%20the%20roughly%202%2C262%20Indian%20employees%20surveyed%20said%20they%20were%20thriving%20at%20their%20workplace%2C%20compared%20with%2034%25%20of%20the%20128%2C278%20employees%20surveyed%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHephzibah%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20both%20Indian-owned%20and%20multinational%20companies%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20multiple%20colleagues%20had%20left%20or%20requested%20transfers%20outside%20India%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20because%20of%20the%20work%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20found%20cultural%20differences%20when%20conducting%20training%20sessions%20for%20employees%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20implementing%20the%20Indian%20training%20schedule%20for%20one%20company's%20American%20employees%2C%20Hephzibah%20faced%20pushback%20on%20issues%20like%20late%20session%20timings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%2C%20'We're%20not%20going%20to%20work%20after%206%20and%20they%20could%20clearly%20call%20it%20out%20without%20feeling%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Hephzibah%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20in%20India%20is%20that%20people%20get%20scared%20to%20speak%20up%20because%20their%20jobs%20might%20be%20impacted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1e23a63-b3a5-4dfe-9fda-a228d77f5f16%5C%22%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hephzibah's%20opinion%2C%20overtime%20and%20vacation%20policies%20need%20to%20be%20strictly%20enforceable%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOutside%2C%20we're%20very%20careful%20to%20communicate%20that%20we%20care%20because%20they%20have%20legal%20backing%20to%20sue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%20here%2C%20that%20entire%20system%20is%20missing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20agreed%20with%20Chang%20that%20effecting%20systemic%20change%20would%20also%20be%20up%20to%20the%20leaders%20and%20middle%20management%2C%20and%20not%20just%20down%20to%20a%20country's%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20leadership%20believing%20in%3F%20Is%20leadership%20overworking%3F%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20if%20they%20are%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20overwork%20their%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-tough-work-culture-under-spotlight-death-ey-employee-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727341634000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f1639fd17aa3c7b2b4e3ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-tough-work-culture-under-spotlight-death-ey-employee-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fourteen-hour%20work%20days%2C%20meetings%20during%20vacations%2C%20and%20no%20overtime.%20India%20has%20one%20of%20the%20tou