s%20was%20the%202013%20comedy%20%26quot%3BThe%20Internship.%26quot%3B%20One%20day%2C%20after%20watching%20Vince%20Vaughn%20and%20Owen%20Wilson%20parade%20around%20Silicon%20Valley%20for%20the%20millionth%20time%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20Baltimore%20was%20my%20hometown%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20it%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20offer%20the%20job%20opportunities%20of%20a%20top-tier%20city.%20I%20felt%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20that%20if%20I%20wanted%20a%20coveted%20job%20at%20Google%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20get%20it.%20I%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20days%20convincing%20myself%20that%20I%20wasn't%20crazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b50d63d2-863b-4458-b130-99f4226b516c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20emptied%20my%20house%2C%20sold%20my%20car%2C%20and%20hopped%20on%20a%20one-way%20flight%20to%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20said%20goodbye%20to%20everything%20I%20had%20ever%20known.%20I%20had%20never%20visited%20San%20Francisco%20and%20arrived%20without%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20I%20had%20a%20job%20lined%20up%20with%20PwC%2C%20but%20that%20was%20always%20meant%20to%20be%20temporary.%20Once%20I%20got%20my%20bearings%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20I%20would%20start%20chasing%20after%20the%20dream%20job%20for%20which%20I%20uprooted%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20to%20get%20hit%20with%20a%20reality%20check.%20The%20recruiters%20at%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Facebook%20wouldn't%20give%20me%20the%20time%20of%20day.%20I%20had%20never%20worked%20for%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%20and%20needed%20additional%20experience%20before%20the%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20would%20take%20me%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20accepted%20an%20offer%20with%20Walmart's%20e-commerce%20team%20in%20San%20Bruno%20to%20do%20financial%20reporting.%20One%20of%20my%20highlights%20was%20supporting%20the%20launch%20of%20Walmart's%20two-day%20shipping%20initiative%20to%20compete%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fis-amazon-prime-worth-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20the%20type%20of%20work%20experience%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20on%20Big%20Tech's%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20I%20was%20back%20interviewing%20with%20all%20the%20heavy%20hitters%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%3A%20Facebook%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Salesforce%2C%20Uber%2C%20Tesla%2C%20etc.%20I%20mostly%20secured%20these%20interviews%20by%20initiating%20a%20discussion%20with%20recruiters%20on%20LinkedIn.%20I%20fine-tuned%20my%20approach%20with%20every%20failed%20interview%20and%20started%20seeing%20repeated%20success.%20I'd%20later%20share%20my%20strategies%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mikefromaccounting.com%2Fstore-1%2Fp%2Fno-flux-given%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaybook%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20wrote%20and%20illustrated%2C%20where%20I%20help%20other%20stuck%20accountants%20land%20their%20dream%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20found%20myself%20knocking%20on%20Google's%20door%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220d86a68-48e2-4d13-afbb-700677a1d303%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20a%20rigorous%20two-month%20interview%20process%2C%20my%20desire%20to%20work%20at%20Google%20became%20a%20reality%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202017%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20offered%20me%20a%20senior%20accountant%20position%20with%20a%20lucrative%20compensation%20package%20that%20included%20a%20sign-on%20bonus%2C%20a%20six-figure%20salary%2C%20an%20annual%20performance%20bonus%20of%2010%25%20or%20more%20of%20my%20salary%2C%20and%20stock%20awards.%20The%20perks%20were%20as%20good%20as%20advertised%2C%20and%20Google%20met%20my%20expectations%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-hired-me-without-college-degree-imposter-syndrome-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edream%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20commute%2C%20however%2C%20was%20more%20like%20a%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20required%20to%20work%20from%20the%20Sunnyvale%20office%2C%20up%20to%20two%20hours%20from%20where%20I%20lived%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20I%20had%20moved%20across%20the%20country%20for%20my%20dream%20job%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20let%20a%20four-hour%20daily%20commute%20stop%20me%20now.%20I%20spent%20the%20next%20year%20commuting%2020%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20a%20corporate%20shuttle%20bus%2C%20and%20it%20was%20grueling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20leave%20my%20apartment%20at%206%3A30%20a.m.%20and%20head%20toward%20the%20bus%20stop.%20My%20workday%20started%20the%20moment%20I%20stepped%20onto%20the%20bus.%20When%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20office%20around%209%20a.m.%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20already%20worked%20a%20half%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20do%20the%20same%20two-hour%20commute%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20leaving%20Sunnyvale%20at%205%20p.m.%20and%20returning%20to%20San%20Francisco%20at%207%20p.m.%20The%20hefty%20commute%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20late%20dinners%2C%20an%20achy%20back%2C%20and%20limited%20time%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212e6b3f1-2a82-4295-ad3b-6571130ee967%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20I%20volunteered%20for%20a%20transfer%20to%20Chicago%20to%20help%20with%20an%20office%20expansion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20leaving%20the%20so-called%20Bay%20Area%20%26quot%3Bmothership%26quot%3B%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20risky%20move.%20I%20knew%20I'd%20miss%20beautiful%20San%20Francisco%20and%20the%20buzzing%20energy%20of%20working%20in%20the%20world's%20tech%20capital.%20I%20also%20knew%20Chicago%20was%20an%20amazing%20city%2C%20with%20a%20more%20manageable%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20closer%20proximity%20to%20my%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20my%20heart%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20but%20Chicago%20is%20my%20kind%20of%20town.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-and-advice-for-first-time-homebuyer-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20started%20a%20family%2C%20and%20shaved%2015%20hours%20off%20my%20weekly%20commute.%20I%20take%20the%20train%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%20and%20spend%20the%20rest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-fears-impacting-kids-parenting-remote-work-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20now%20have%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20relax%2C%20and%20I%20can%20sit%20down%20with%20my%20family%20for%20dinner%20at%20a%20more%20reasonable%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb9cbc66-29b0-4f56-9375-dd2b6721d258%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaving%20the%20mothership%20hasn't%20slowed%20me%20down%20a%20bit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20promoted%20to%20manager%20in%202020%20and%20now%20lead%20an%20accounting%20team%20supporting%20Google%20Search%20and%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20feeling%20stuck%20in%20their%20career%2C%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20take%20some%20risks%20and%20make%20some%20sacrifices.%20I%20ultimately%20had%20to%20bounce%20around%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20West%20Coast%2C%20and%20Midwest%20to%20find%20the%20pleasant%20and%20fulfilling%20career%20I%20sought%2C%20but%20I%20found%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20by%20uprooting%20my%20life%20and%20commuting%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20for%20my%20dream%20job%20at%20Google%2C%20and%20it%20was%20totally%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWant%20to%20share%20your%20story%3F%20Email%20Lauryn%20Haas%20at%20lhaas%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-job-google-great-perks-nightmare-commute-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727341502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f44a1cde59ade1a3b48f85%3Fformat%3