0to%20rival%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20AI%20chips%2C%20but%20AWS's%20offerings%20have%20wider%20availability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAWS's%20regional%20availability%20offers%20customers%20more%20options%2C%20potentially%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20tech%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-cloud-ai-anthropic-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%3C%2Fa%3E%20providers%20have%20been%20investing%20in%20their%20own%20homegrown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-frontier-crowded-winners-losers-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20chips%20lately%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20replicating%20Nvidia's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-models-bedrock-service-success-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20Web%20Services%20have%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainium%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Inferentia%20processors%20for%20several%20years%2C%20while%20Google%20unveiled%20its%20sixth%20generation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ai-google-data-centers-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETPU%3C%2Fa%3E%20line%20of%20AI%20chips%20this%20year.%20Microsoft%20also%20introduced%20its%20first%20in-house%20AI%20accelerator%2C%20Maia%2C%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20still%20be%20too%20early%20to%20tell%20which%20company%20is%20doing%20better%2C%20given%20the%20lack%20of%20financial%20disclosure%20by%20each%20company%20and%20Nvidia's%20dominance%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpu-rich-vs-gpu-poor-tech-companies-in-each-group-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20a%20tech%20analyst%20at%20D.A.%20Davidson%2C%20AWS's%20AI%20chips%20may%20have%20one%20potential%20advantage%3A%20more%20regional%20availability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS's%20Inferentia%2C%20which%20is%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-may-lose-ai-inference-market-groq-cerebras-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einference%3C%2Fa%3E%20stage%20of%20AI%2C%20is%20more%20widely%20available%20than%20Google's%20competing%20v5e%20TPU%20chips%2C%20according%20to%20data%20shared%20by%20Luria%20in%20a%20research%20note%20this%20week.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS's%20AI%20training%20chip%2C%20Trainium%2C%20also%20had%20a%20higher%20rate%20of%20regional%20availability%20than%20its%20TPU%20counterpart.%20Microsoft's%20Maia%20has%20no%20external%20deployment%20because%20it%20currently%20only%20serves%20OpenAI-related%20workloads%2C%20Luria%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20Chips%20regional%20deployment%20rate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f350f9cfb7f307e574af21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERegional%20deployment%20rate%20of%20AI%20chips%20by%20Microsoft%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Google%3Cp%3ED.A.%20Davidson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20these%20chips%20available%20in%20more%20regions%20is%20important%20because%20it%20gives%20customers%20a%20diversity%20of%20options%2C%20Luria%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Not%20every%20customer%20needs%20Nvidia's%20GPUs%2C%20which%20can%20be%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20than%20other%20processors%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20high%20level%20of%20availability%20of%20home-grown%20chips%20at%20AWS%20data%20centers%20means%20they%20can%20give%20their%20customers%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%20%26quot%3BCustomers%20with%20very%20demanding%20training%20needs%20may%20choose%20to%20use%20a%20cluster%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%20at%20the%20AWS%20data%20center%2C%20and%20customers%20with%20more%20straightforward%20needs%20can%20use%20Amazon%20chips%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20spokesperson%20Patrick%20Neighorn%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20strive%20to%20provide%20customers%20the%20choice%20of%20compute%20that%20best%20meets%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20workload%2C%20and%20we're%20encouraged%20by%20the%20progress%20we're%20making%20with%20AWS%20silicon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20kind%20of%20edge%20would%20be%20important%20for%20AWS.%20The%20company%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20its%20silicon%20business%20lately%2C%20but%20its%20AI%20chips%20have%20so%20far%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseen%20mixed%20results%20against%20Nvidia's%20dominance.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It's%20early%20days%20still%2C%20though.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20point%20may%20have%20some%20flaws.%20For%20example%2C%20AWS's%20first%20Inferentia%20offering%20launched%20in%202018%2C%20while%20Google's%20latest%20TPU%20v5e%20and%20v5p%20chips%20became%20available%20within%20the%20past%20year%2C%20meaning%20AWS's%20chip%20had%20more%20time%20to%20reach%20its%20current%20deployment%20level.%20Some%20would%20also%20argue%20that%20regional%20deployment%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20sign%20of%20effectiveness%2C%20as%20some%20customers%20prefer%20having%20chip%20capacity%20concentrated%20in%20a%20single%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuria%20wrote%20in%20his%20note%20that%20Google's%20TPU%20v5e%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20mature%20accelerator%20offering%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20three%20largest%20cloud%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20broader%20point%20is%20that%20AWS%20and%20Google%2