3EOnce%20training%20a%20model%20is%20done%2C%20inference%20chips%20produce%20the%20outputs%20and%20complete%20tasks%20based%20on%20that%20training%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20generating%20a%20picture%20or%20written%20answers%20to%20a%20prompt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsambanova-ceo-rodrigo-liang-nvidia-artificial-intelligence-startup-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERodrigo%20Liang%20cofounded%20SambaNova%3C%2Fa%3E%20Systems%20in%202017%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20going%20after%20Nvidia's%20already%20obvious%20lead.%20But%20back%20then%2C%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20ecosystem%20was%20even%20younger%2C%20and%20inference%20loads%20were%20tiny.%20With%20foundation%20models%20advancing%20in%20size%20and%20accuracy%2C%20the%20flip%20from%20training%20machine%20learning%20models%20to%20using%20them%20is%20coming%20into%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Nvidia%20CFO%20Colleen%20Kress%20said%20the%20company's%20data%20center%20workloads%20had%20reached%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-may-lose-ai-inference-market-groq-cerebras-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40%25%20inference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Liang%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20expects%2090%25%20of%20AI%20computing%20workloads%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20be%20in%20inference%20in%20the%20not-too-distant%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20several%20startups%20are%20charging%20aggressively%20into%20the%20inference%20market%20%E2%80%94%20emphasizing%20where%20they%20might%20outperform%20the%20goliath%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESambaNova%20uses%20a%20reconfigurable%20dataflow%20unit%20or%20RDU%20instead%20of%20Nvidia's%20and%20AMD's%20graphics%20processing%20units.%20Liang's%20firm%20purports%20that%20its%20architecture%20is%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20machine%20learning%20models%20since%20it%20was%20designed%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20and%20not%20for%20rendering%20graphics.%2