%20SambaNova%20claim%20to%20offer%20the%20fastest%20inference%20computing%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20neither%20use%20GPUs%2C%20the%20type%20of%20chip%20leaders%20Nvidia%20and%20AMD%20promote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SambaNova%2C%20its%20RDUs%20are%20ideal%20for%20agentic%20AI%2C%20which%20can%20complete%20functions%20without%20much%20instruction.%20Speed%20is%20an%20important%20factor%20when%20multiple%20AI%20models%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20and%20waiting%20for%20an%20answer%20can%20dampen%20the%20magic%20of%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20isn't%20just%20one%20measure%20of%20inference%20speed.%20The%20specifications%20of%20each%20model%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-open-source-ai-platforms-future-competition-apple-llama-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Llama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-ai-company-amazon-betting-billions-on-anthropic-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-new-o1-model-capabilities-agi-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20o1%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20determine%20how%20fast%20results%20are%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeed%20in%20AI%20computing%20results%20from%20several%20engineering%20factors%20that%20go%20beyond%20the%20chip%20itself.%20And%20the%20way%20chips%20are%20networked%20together%20can%20impact%20their%20performance%2C%20which%20means%20Nvidia%20chips%20in%20one%20data%20center%20may%20perform%20differently%20than%20the%20same%20chip%20in%20another%20data%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20tokens%20per%20second%20that%20can%20be%20consumed%20(when%20a%20prompt%20goes%20in)%20and%20generated%20(when%20a%20response%20comes%20out)%20is%20a%20common%20metric%20for%20AI%20computing%20speed.%20Tokens%20are%20a%20base%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunit%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20data%2C%20where%20data%20could%20be%20pixels%2C%20words%2C%20audio%2C%20and%20beyond.%20But%20tokens%20per%20second%20don't%20account%20for%20latency%20or%20lag%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20stem%20from%20multiple%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20difficult%20to%20make%20an%20apples-to-apples%20comparison%20between%20hardware%20as%20performance%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edepends%20on%20how%20the%20hardware%20is%20set%20up%20and%20the%20software%20that%20runs%20it.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20models%20themselves%20are%20improving%20constantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hopes%20of%20advancing%20the%20market%20for%20inference%20faster%2C%20and%20edge%20their%20way%20into%20a%20market%20dominated%20by%20Nvidia%2C%20several%20newer%20hardware%20companies%20are%20trying%20different%20business%20models%20to%20bypass%20direct%20competition%20with%20Nvidia%20and%20go%20straight%20to%20the%20companies%20building%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESambaNova%20offers%20Meta's%20open-source%20Llama%20foundation%20model%20through%20its%20cloud%20service%20and%20Cerebras%20and%20Groq%20have%20launched%20similar%20services.%20Thus%2C%20these%20companies%20are%20competing%20with%20both%20chip%20design%20companies%20like%20Nvidia%20and%20AI%20foundation%20model%20companies%20like%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificialanalysis.ai%20provides%20public%20information%20comparing%20models%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoffer%20inference-as-a-service%20via%20API.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20site%20showed%20that%20Cerebras%2C%20SambaNova%2C%20and%20Groq%20were%20indeed%20the%20three%20fastest%20APIs%20for%20Met'a's%20Llama%203.1%2070B%20and%208B%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20isn't%20included%20in%20this%20comparison%20because%20the%20company%20doesn't%20provide%20inference-as-a-service.%20MLPerf%20shares%20inference%20performance%20benchmarks%20for%20hardware%20computing%20speed.%20Nvidia%20is%20among%20the%20best%20