v%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fdhpn5cf_suicide_625x300_26_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20suicides%20among%20students%20have%20captured%20the%20news%20cycle%20and%20the%20public's%20attention.%20Kota%2C%20India's%20infamous%20'coaching%20hub'%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20fixation.%20Stories%20about%20the%20tragic%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20among%20young%20students%20and%20policy%20measures%20to%20identify%20and%20support%20students%20who%20exhibit%20signs%20of%20suicide%20risk%20have%20become%20commonplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20report%20underscored%20the%20growing%20concern.%20The%20number%20of%20suicides%20among%20students%20saw%20a%20drastic%20rise%20of%2021%25%20between%202019%20and%202020%2C%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%204.5%25%20from%202020%20to%202021.%20The%20data%20paints%20a%20grim%20picture%20that%20extends%20beyond%20Kota%20and%20its%20intense%20coaching%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Unprecedented%20Spike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20suicide%20rate%20has%20been%20growing%20at%20an%20unprecedented%20rate%20-%20one%20that%20was%20not%20seen%20earlier%2C%20in%20the%20last%20six%20decades%20since%20data%20was%20collected.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20National%20Crimes%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20reported%201.71%20lakh%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20as%20many%20as%2040%25%20of%20these%20deaths%20were%20among%20children%20and%20young%20people.%20If%20we%20take%20a%20closer%20look%2C%20around%2010%2C000%20young%20people%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20took%20their%20lives%20in%202022.%20Generally%2C%20more%20men%20die%20by%20suicide%20as%20compared%20to%20women%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20within%20this%20age%20group%2C%20we%20observe%20a%20skew%20in%20the%20data%2C%20where%2055%25%20of%20suicide%20deaths%20were%20reported%20among%20girls%20and%20young%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20between%2018%20and%2030%20years%20of%20age%20accounted%20for%2030%25%20of%20all%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20Consistently%2C%20more%20men%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20this%20age%20group%20than%20women%20-%20typically%2C%2065%25%20men%20compared%20to%2035%25%20women.%20However%2C%20suicides%20among%20young%20women%20increased%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%20-%2012%25%20-%20as%20compared%20to%20a%201%25%20rise%20among%20young%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Host%20Of%20Factors%20Drive%20Youth%20To%20Take%20Their%20Lives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20be%20answered%20in%20part%20by%20understanding%20the%20forces%20and%20drivers%20that%20shape%20young%20people's%20mental%20health%20and%20well-being.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20landscape%20study%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20answer%20this%20exact%20question.%20The%20study%2C%20funded%20by%20the%20Being%20initiative%2C%20involved%20a%20host%20of%20consultations%20and%20research%20activities%20with%20young%20people%2C%20mental%20health%20experts%2C%20development%20professionals%2C%20funders%20and%20policymakers%20across%20the%20country%20from%20diverse%20geographies%2C%20identities%20and%20contexts.%20Through%20this%20landscape%20analysis%2C%20we%20uncovered%20a%20myriad%20of%20personal%2C%20social%20and%20environmental%20factors%20that%20influence%20mental%20health%20and%20well-being%20for%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Widening%20Generational%20Divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influence%20of%20family%2C%20both%20positive%20and%20negative%2C%20emerged%20frequently%20as%20a%20factor%20that%20impacts%20young%20people's%20mental%20health.%20Those%20we%20spoke%20to%20stressed%20the%20growing%20generational%20divide%20among%20young%20people%20and%20their%20parents.%20The%20constant%20tussle%20for%20autonomy%20in%20decisions%20around%20education%2C%20careers%20and%20relationships%20weighed%20on%20them%3B%20they%20expressed%20being%20misunderstood%20by%20their%20parents%20and%20unable%20to%20bridge%20the%20generational%20communication%20gap%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20deeply%20impacted%20by%20the%20family%20environments%20in%20which%20they%20were%20raised.%20They%20reported%20conflict%20and%20marital%20discord%20among%20parents%2C%20neglect%20and%20abuse%20and%20poor%20parental%20mental%20health%2C%20all%20of%20which%20had%20a%20direct%20consequence%20on%20their%20well-being.%20This%20instability%20in%20family%20relationships%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20young%20people%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20suicide%20data%20from%20NCRB.%20Among%20the%2069%2C000%20cases%20of%20young%20people%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20(18-30%20and%20below%2018%20years)%20in%202022%2C%20over%2030%25%20reported%20family%20problems%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Gender%20Quandary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20women%20we%20spoke%20to%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20added%20burden%20of%20gendered%20expectations%20from%20families%20and%20society.%20Patriarchal%20notions%20of%20a%20woman's%20role%20and%20responsibilities%20within%20the%20household%20are%20internalised%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age.%20Young%20women%20learn%20early%20on%20to%20deprioritise%20their%20needs%20and%20ambitions%20as%20compared%20to%20their%20male%20siblings%20or%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20this%20control%20extends%20to%20restrictions%20and%20policing%20of%20women's%20bodies%20and%20mobility%20-%20from%20deciding%20what%20young%20women%20wear%20and%20who%20they%20socialise%20with%2C%20to%20limiting%20their%20access%20to%20certain%20places%20when%20menstruating%20and%20controlling%20how%20many%20children%20they%20should%20have.%20The%20relationship%20between%20gender%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20and%20suicide%20in%20India%20needs%20further%20unpacking%3A%20It%20is%20disconcerting%20that%20suicide%20is%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20among%20young%20women%20in%20India%20between%20the%20age%20of%2015-29%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20State%20Of%20Education%20And%20Employment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20pervasive%20yet%20under-reported%20issue%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20support%20within%20education%20and%20workplace%20settings%20for%20young%20people%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds.%20Young%20people%20reported%20experiences%20of%20institutional%20discrimination%20based%20on%20their%20identities%20of%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20gender%20and%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20which%20compounds%20mental%20health%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20overlooked%20in%20the%20conversation%20on%20student%20suicides%20are%20working%20children%20and%20youth%20who%20have%20dropped%20out%20of%20schools%20or%20colleges.%20Employed%20in%20the%20informal%20sector%2C%20they%20face%20precarious%20working%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20amenities%2C%20safety%20measures%20and%20protections%20from%20violence%20and%20discrimination.%20Young%20people%20frequently%20migrate%20to%20urban%20cities%20for%20better%20opportunities.%20In%20this%20unfamiliar%20environment%2C%20they%20encounter%20isolation%2C%20language%20barriers%2C%20and%20skill%20gap%20challenges%2C%20and%20are%20left%20to%20cope%20by%20themselves%20without%20adequate%20social%20or%20institutional%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Digital%20Boom%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20digital%20boom%20where%20smartphone%20and%20internet%20use%20has%20had%20a%20consequential%20and%20lasting%20impact%20on%20young%20people.%20Cyberbullying%2C%20digital%20addiction%2C%20misinformation%20and%20harmful%20portrayals%20of%20mental%20health%20and%20suicide%20in%20the%20media%20-%20including%20social%20media%20-%20have%20led%20to%20distress%20and%20unsafe%20behaviour%20among%20young%20people%2C%20who%20are%20left%20to%20negotiate%20these%20complex%20systems%20while%20confronting%20their%20generational%20challenges%20of%20growing%20socio-economic%20inequality%2C%20conflicts%20and%20climate%20change.%20The%20confluence%20of%20these%20interlinked%20drivers%20and%20forces%20places%20young%20people%20in%20a%20unique%20predicament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Do%20We%20Go%20From%20Here%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20of%20India's%20youth%20is%20immense%20and%20their%20lived%20experiences%20and%20needs%20are%20highly%20diverse.%20Tackling%20these%20complex%20and%20cross-cutting%20issues%20requires%20building%20and%20strengthening%20collaboration%20among%20stakeholders%20to%20develop%20a%20shared%20understanding%20of%20youth%20mental%20health%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20prevention%20of%20suicide.%20Services%2C%20policies%20and%20programmes%20should%20be%20made%20youth-friendly%20and%20inclusive%20of%20these%20diverse%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecific%20policy%20and%20structural%20recommendations%20include%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ecreating%20and%20promoting%20interventions%20that%20strengthen%20familial%20relationships%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%20and%20communication%2C%20as%20well%20as%20addressing%20gender%20norms%20and%20dysfunction%20perpetuated%20by%20family%20systems%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eneed%20for%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20create%20enabling%20environments%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20students%20from%20all%20backgrounds%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eenforcing%20guidelines%20for%20the%20media%20on%20reporting%20or%20engaging%20with%20content%20on%20suicides%3B%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eaddressing%20youth%20unemployment%20by%20enabling%20young%20people%20to%20access%20stable%20and%20viable%20career%20pathways%2C%20thus%20offering%20a%20chance%20at%20upward%20mobility%20and%20the%20associated%20autonomy%20and%20freedoms%20it%20offers%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20attention%20of%20World%20Suicide%20Prevention%20Day%2C%20suicide%20prevention%20requires%20a%20consistent%2C%20multisectoral%20response%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20safeguard%20the%20country's%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BTanya%20Nicole%20Fernandes%20and%20Amiti%20Varma%20are%20research%20fellows%3B%20Dr%20Soumitra%20Pathare%20is%20a%20consultant%20psychiatrist%20and%20director%3B%20all%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Mental%20Health%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Policy%20(CMHLP)%2C%20Indian%20Law%20Society%2C%20India.%20%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20joint%20collaborative%20study%20by%20CMHLP%20and%20Sangath%20Addictions%20and%20related-Research%20Group.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727333820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fntito61o_ai_625x300_26_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffamily-job-discrimination-whats-driving-indian-youth-to-suicide-6652878%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20we%20spoke%20to%20stressed%20the%20growing%20generational%20divide%20among%20young%20people%20and%20their%20parents.%20The%20constant%20tussle%20for%20autonomy%20in%20decisions%20around%20education%2C%20careers%20and%20relationships%20weighed%20on%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffamily-job-discrimination-whats-driving-indian-youth-to-suicide-6652878%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Online%20Gaming%20App%2C%20Promise%20Of%20Big%20Prizes%20And%20A%20Rs%20400-Crore%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20against%20an%20online%20gaming%20app%20has%20led%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20to%20a%20Rs%20400-crore%20fraud%20involving%20Chinese%20nationals.%20The%20ED%20has%20now%20frozen%20the%20accounts%20of%20some%20Chinese%20nationals%20linked%20to%20the%20online%20gaming%20app%2C%20Fiewin.%20A%20sum%20of%20about%20Rs%2025%20crore%20has%20been%20frozen.%20Earlier%2C%20four%20Indians%20who%20allegedly%20supported%20the%20Chinese%20nationals%20in%20the%20fraud%20were%20arrested%20by%20officials%20of%20ED%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20ED%20was%20supported%20by%20Binance%2C%20which%20operates%20the%20world's%20largest%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20in%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpnq9d3p_fiewin_625x300_26_September_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Fiewin%20Fraud%20Worked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fiewin%20app%20gained%20traction%20by%20promising%20users%20the%20opportunity%20to%20earn%20money%20easily%20by%20playing%20mini-games%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Binance%20statement.%20%26quot%3BNew%20users%20could%20quickly%20create%20an%20account%20and%20begin%20participating%20in%20the%20app's%20activities%2C%20with%20the%20option%20to%20'top%20up'%20their%20in-app%20balance%20via%20various%20payment%20methods.%20However%2C%20reports%20have%20surfaced%20suggesting%20that%20once%20users'%20accounts%20accumulated%20substantial%20funds%2C%20the%20app%20stopped%20allowing%20them%20to%20withdraw%20the%20funds%2C%20leaving%20them%20unable%20to%20recover%20their%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20probe%20found%20that%20a%20sum%20of%20about%20Rs%20400%20crore%20was%20stolen%20through%20this%20scheme.%20%26quot%3BThis%20money%20was%20transferred%20into%20various%20cryptocurrency%20addresses%2C%20which%20were%20later%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20Binance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20people%20got%20duped%20by%20this%20online%20gaming%20app%2C%20local%20police%20started%20receiving%20complaints.%20The%20number%20of%20such%20complaints%20grew%2C%20and%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20specialised%20in%20economic%20crimes%20and%20money%20laundering%20cases.%20The%20ED's%20investigation%20found%20Chinese%20nationals%20were%20operating%20this%20fraud%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20connections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20found%20that%20the%20money%20collected%20from%20games%20would%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20accounts%20of%20some%20people%20called%20%26quot%3Brecharge%20persons%26quot%3B.%20These%20people%20allowed%20their%20accounts%20to%20be%20used%20in%20exchange%20for%20some%20commission%20from%20the%20app%20owners.%20This%20sum%20was%20then%20converted%20to%20cryptocurrency%20and%20transferred%20to%20crypto%20accounts%20of%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20ED%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20ED%20discovered%20that%20the%20app%20had%20been%20part%20of%20a%20cross-border%20criminal%20network%20it%20used%20various%20methods%20to%20obfuscate%20the%20origin%20and%20movement%20of%20illicit%20funds%20by%20utilizing%20bank%20accounts%20of%20'mules'%20and%20cryptocurrency%20wallets%2C%20creating%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20transactions%20to%20hinder%20detection%20and%20tracing%2C%26quot%3B%20Binance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpullmrno_fiewin_625x300_26_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Accused%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20investigation%20found%20that%20Arun%20Sahu%20and%20Alok%20Sahu%20from%20Odisha's%20Rourkela%20were%20%26quot%3Brecharge%20persons%26quot%3B.%20The%20money%20collected%20from%20online%20gamers%20would%20come%20to%20their%20accounts.%20This%20money%20would%20then%20be%20converted%20to%20cryptocurrency%20and%20deposited%20into%20the%20online%20wallets%20of%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20arrested%20accused%2C%20Patna%20engineer%20Chetan%20Prakash%2C%20allegedly%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20converting%20money%20in%20recharge%20persons'%20accounts%20to%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Stalin%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%20from%20Chennai%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection.%20Stalin%20allegedly%20helped%20Pie%20Pengyun%2C%20a%20Chinese%20national%20based%20in%20Gansu%20province%2C%20become%20a%20co-director%20in%20a%20company%20he%20owned.%20ED%20has%20found%20that%20Pengyun%20used%20the%20account%20of%20Stalin's%20company%20Studio%2021%20for%20bulk%20payout%20services%20related%20to%20the%20app.%20This%20helped%20them%20gain%20the%20confidence%20of%20online%20gamers%20in%20the%20beginning%20and%20prompted%20them%20to%20place%20larger%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20has%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20several%20individuals%20who%20played%20key%20roles%20in%20facilitating%20the%20fraud%2C%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20handlers%20linked%20to%20Fiewin's%20gaming%20apps.%20The%20criminals%20communicated%20via%20privacy-focused%20messaging%20applications%20and%20operated%20from%20various%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20Binance%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Massive%20Fraud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20so%20far%20has%20found%20that%20a%20sum%20of%20nearly%20Rs%20400%20crore%20has%20been%20laundered%20using%20the%20Fiewin%20app.%20This%20amount%20was%20deposited%20in%20the%20form%20of%20cryptocurrency%20in%20eight%20Binance%20wallets%20belonging%20to%20Chinese%20nationals.%20These%20nationals%2C%20ED%20has%20found%2C%20communicated%20with%20the%20Indian%20accused%20--%20Arun%20Sahu%2C%20Alok%20Sahu%2C%20Chetan%20Prakash%20and%20Joseph%20Stalin%20--%20through%20the%20Telegram%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20case%20still%20ongoing%2C%20both%20the%20ED%20and%20Binance%20continue%20to%20work%20closely%20to%20further%20untangle%20the%20criminal%20network%20behind%20the%20fraud%20scheme.%20Their%20combined%20efforts%20aim%20to%20expose%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20Fiewin%20app's%20fraudulent%20activities%20and%20identify%20everyone%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Binance%20has%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727333700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Flgg59hb_mobile-phone-generic-pixabay_625x300_08_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffiewin-enforcement-directorate-how-gaming-app-linked-to-chinese-nationals-was-used-for-rs-400-crore-fraud-6652673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20investigation%20against%20an%20online%20gaming%20app%20has%20led%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20to%20a%20Rs%20400-crore%20fraud%20in