e%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fh4fnv3c_ai_625x300_26_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20wrestling%20with%20a%20question%20that%20many%20are%20asking%3A%20are%20we%20already%20in%20an%20AI%20bubble%3F%20And%20if%20we%20are%2C%20what%20does%20that%20mean%20for%20India%3F%20To%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20where%20we%20stand%2C%20we%20first%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20global%20picture%20-%20because%20that's%20where%20the%20story%20of%20AI's%20present%20and%20future%20is%20being%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20pieces%20got%20me%20thinking.%20The%20first%2C%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlights%20how%20the%20investor%20frenzy%20around%20AI%20might%20be%20cooling%20off.%20Some%20of%20the%20biggest%20AI%20companies%20have%20seen%20their%20stock%20prices%20dip%20by%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20in%20the%20last%20month%20alone.%20And%20here's%20the%20real%20kicker%3A%20only%20about%204.8%25%20of%20American%20companies%20currently%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20products%20or%20services%2C%20down%20from%20earlier%20this%20year.%20That's%20a%20shocking%20statistic%2C%20given%20all%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20report%20titled%2C%20'%3Cem%3EGen%20AI%3A%20Too%20Much%20Spend%2C%20Too%20Little%20Benefit%3F'.%3C%2Fem%3E%20In%20it%2C%20Jim%20Covello%2C%20the%20Head%20of%20Global%20Equity%20Research%2C%20points%20out%20something%20we%20should%20all%20be%20paying%20attention%20to%3A%20over%20%241%20trillion%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20spent%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20development%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20But%20will%20it%20be%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovello's%20not%20convinced.%20He%20argues%20that%20for%20AI%20to%20justify%20that%20level%20of%20spending%2C%20it%20has%20to%20tackle%20some%20really%20complex%20problems%20-%20ones%20it's%20not%20quite%20ready%20to%20solve.%20Developing%20and%20running%20AI%20isn't%20cheap.%20Unlike%20other%20tech%20shifts%20that%20helped%20cut%20costs%2C%20AI%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20bringing%20down%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20big%20question%20is%20-%20will%20these%20massive%20investments%20ever%20pay%20off%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20High%20Price%20Of%20An%20AI%20Query%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20training%20models%20like%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20consume%20massive%20amounts%20of%20energy%20-%20enough%20to%20power%2050%20American%20homes%20for%20a%20century.%20Costs%20for%20training%20these%20models%20are%20skyrocketing%3A%20current%20estimates%20for%20the%20biggest%20models%20hit%20%24100%20million%2C%20with%20future%20generations%20potentially%20reaching%20%241%20billion%20or%20even%20%2410%20billion.%20The%20operational%20costs%20-%20answering%20queries%2C%20for%20instance%20-%20can%20also%20balloon%2C%20costing%20up%20to%20%24223%2C000%20for%20tasks%20like%20summarising%20financial%20reports.%20This%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20for%20investors%20despite%20the%20%2495%20billion%20already%20poured%20into%20AI%20startups%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here's%20where%20things%20get%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnter%20Entrepreneurial%20Optimism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20scepticism%2C%20the%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%20around%20AI%20refuses%20to%20slow%20down.%20Just%20look%20at%20Mukesh%20Bansal%2C%20a%20veteran%20entrepreneur%20who%20recently%20launched%20Nurix.ai%20and%20secured%20%2427%20million%20in%20funding.%20Mukesh%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20building%20successful%20ventures%2C%20and%20his%20leap%20into%20AI%20signals%20a%20strong%20belief%20in%20its%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20me%20to%20a%20broader%20observation%3A%20we%20might%20be%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20Indian%20AI%20startups%20ready%20to%20go%20global%2C%20much%20like%20the%20SaaS%20boom%20we%20witnessed%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20These%20startups%20are%20not%20just%20riding%20a%20hype%20train%3B%20they%20aim%20to%20solve%20real-world%20problems%20and%20bring%20tangible%20value%20to%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20this%20massive%20wave%20of%20AI%20tools%20and%20generative%20AI%20tech%20is%20hitting%20the%20market%2C%20putting%20powerful%20capabilities%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20everyday%20users.%20It's%20democratising%20intelligence%20like%20never%20before%20-%20people%20can%20now%20tap%20into%20tools%20that%20were%20once%20only%20accessible%20to%20experts%20or%20big%20corporations.%20So%2C%20while%20billions%20-maybe%20even%20trillions%20-%20are%20being%20sunk%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20there's%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20explore%20and%20use%20these%20tools%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20A%20Middle%20Ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20does%20this%20leave%20us%3F%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20we%20have%20warnings%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%20fueled%20by%20excessive%20spending%20with%20questionable%20returns.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20see%20relentless%20optimism%20from%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors%20betting%20big%20on%20AI's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20lies%20somewhere%20in%20between.%20Yes%2C%20there%20may%20be%20overexuberance%2C%20but%20dismissing%20AI's%20transformative%20potential%20could%20mean%20missing%20out%20on%20significant%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20believe%20we're%20in%20an%20AI%20bubble%3F%20Or%20do%20you%20think%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20AI's%20true%20potential%20being%20realised%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20is%20the%20AI%20Editor%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727331180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqp7k71b8_ai_625x300_26_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-we-already-in-an-ai-bubble-6652600%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20we%20have%20warnings%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%20fueled%20by%20excessive%20spending%20with%20questionable%20returns.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20see%20relentless%20optimism%20from%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors%20betting%20big%20on%20AI's%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-we-already-in-an-ai-bubble-6652600%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt's%20action-packed%20'Jigra'%20trailer%20in%20here!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727331169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113690210%2Cimgsize-30778.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjigra-trailer-alia-bhatt-packs-in-some-impressive-action-in-her-quest-to-save-her-brother-played-by-vedang-raina%2Farticleshow%2F113690249.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113690249.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAfter%20an%20intense%20teaser%20which%20released%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20makers%20have%20now%20unveiled%20the%20full%20trailer%20of%20Jigra.%20It%20showcases%20Alia%20Bhatt%20in%20a%20fierce%20role%20as%20Satya%2C%20a%20devoted%20sister%20who%20will%20stop%20at%20nothing%20to%20save%20her%20brother%2C%20Ankur%2C%20portrayed%20by%20Vedang%20Raina.%20This%20film%20marks%20Raina's%20first%20theatrical%20release%20and%20his%20sec