2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20she's%20leaving%20OpenAI%2C%20where%20she%20was%20chief%20technology%20officer.%20Now%2C%20two%20other%20leaders%20are%20leaving%2C%20according%20to%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20who%20posted%20a%20note%20to%20OpenAI%20staff%20shortly%20after%205%20p.m.%20Pacific%20Time%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Altman%2C%20%26quot%3BBarret%20and%20Bob%26quot%3B%20are%20leaving%20OpenAI.%20Those%20are%20Barret%20Zoph%2C%20who%20had%20served%20as%20the%20company's%20vice%20president%20of%20research%2C%20and%20Bob%20McGrew%2C%20who%20was%20chief%20research%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20about%20the%20departures.%20But%20Zoph%20confirmed%20his%20departure%2C%20posting%20a%20note%20to%20X%20saying%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20OpenAI.%20And%20The%20Verge's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkyliebytes%2Fstatus%2F1839094668593868825%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKylie%20Robison%20posted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20McGrew%20had%20left%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20note%20Altman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F1839093415226524114%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DUm1Cn1fZ4MzFempQTot0yg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20to%20X%20below%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3Ei%20just%20posted%20this%20note%20to%20openai%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EHi%20All%E2%80%93%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMira%20has%20been%20instrumental%20to%20OpenAI's%20progress%20and%20growth%20the%20last%206.5%20years%3B%20she%20has%20been%20a%20hugely%20significant%20factor%20in%20our%20development%20from%20an%20unknown%20research%20lab%20to%20an%20important%20company.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhen%20Mira%20informed%20me%20this%20morning%20that%20she%20was%20leaving%2C%20I%20was%20saddened%20but%20of%20course%20support%20her%20decision.%20For%20the%20past%20year%2C%20she%20has%20been%20building%20out%20a%20strong%20bench%20of%20leaders%20that%20will%20continue%20our%20progress.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20share%20that%20Bob%20and%20Barret%20have%20decided%20to%20depart%20OpenAI.%20Mira%2C%20Bob%2C%20and%20Barret%20made%20these%20decisions%20independently%20of%20each%20other%20and%20amicably%2C%20but%20the%20timing%20of%20Mira's%20decision%20was%20such%20that%20it%20made%20sense%20to%20now%20do%20this%20all%20at%20once%2C%20so%20that%20we%20can%20work%20together%20for%20a%20smooth%20handover%20to%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20leadership.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20am%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20all%20of%20them%20for%20their%20contributions.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBeing%20a%20leader%20at%20OpenAI%20is%20all-consuming.%20On%20one%20hand%20it's%20a%20privilege%20to%20build%20AGI%20and%20be%20the%20fastest-growing%20company%20that%20gets%20to%20put%20our%20advanced%20research%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%20it's%20relentless%20to%20lead%20a%20team%20through%20it%E2%80%94and%20they%20have%20gone%20above%20and%20beyond%20the%20call%20of%20duty%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMark%20is%20going%20to%20be%20our%20new%20SVP%20of%20Research%20and%20will%20now%20lead%20the%20research%20org%20in%20partnership%20with%20Jakub%20as%20Chief%20Scientist.%20This%20has%20been%20our%20long-term%20succession%20plan%20for%20Bob%20someday%3B%20although%20it's%20happening%20sooner%20than%20we%20thought%2C%20I%20couldn't%20be%20more%20excited%20that%20Mark%20is%20stepping%20into%20the%20role.%20Mark%20obviously%20has%20deep%20technical%20expertise%2C%20but%20he%20has%20also%20learned%20how%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20and%20manager%20in%20a%20very%20impressive%20way%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EJosh%20Achiam%20is%20going%20to%20take%20on%20a%20new%20role%20as%20Head%20of%20Mission%20Alignment%2C%20working%20across%20the%20company%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20get%20all%20pieces%20(and%20culture)%20right%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20to%20succeed%20at%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EKevin%20and%20Srinivas%20will%20continue%20to%20lead%20the%20Applied%20team.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMatt%20Knight%20will%20be%20our%20Chief%20Information%20Security%20Officer%20having%20already%20served%20in%20this%20capacity%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20has%20been%20our%20plan%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMark%2C%20Jakub%2C%20Kevin%2C%20Srinivas%2C%20Matt%2C%20and%20Josh%20will%20report%20to%20me.%20I%20have%20over%20the%20past%20year%20or%20so%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20on%20the%20non-technical%20parts%20of%20our%20organization%3B%20I%20am%20now%20looking%20forward%20to%20spending%20most%20of%20my%20time%20on%20the%20technical%20and%20product%20parts%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETonight%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20gather%20at%20575%20starting%20at%205%3A30%20pm.%20Mira%2C%20Bob%2C%20Barret%2C%20and%20Mark%20will%20be%20there.%20This%20will%20be%20about%20showing%20our%20appreciation%20and%20reflecting%20on%20all%20we've%20done%20together.%20Then%20tomorrow%2C%20we%20will%20all%20have%20an%20all-hands%20and%20can%20answer%20any%20questions%20then.%20A%20calendar%20invite%20will%20come%20soon.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ELeadership%20changes%20are%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20companies%2C%20especially%20companies%20that%20grow%20so%20quickly%20and%20are%20so%20demanding.%20I%20obviously%20won't%20pretend%20it's%20natural%20for%20this%20one%20to%20be%20so%20abrupt%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20a%20normal%20company%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20reasons%20Mira%20explained%20to%20me%20(there%20is%20never%20a%20good%20time%2C%20anything%20not%20abrupt%20would%20have%20leaked%2C%20and%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%20this%20while%20OpenAI%20was%20in%20an%20upswing)%20make%20sense.%20We%20can%20both%20talk%20about%20this%20more%20tomorrow%20during%20all-hands.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThank%20you%20for%20all%20of%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESam%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20Check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-note-more-staff-exits-barret-bob-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727311866000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6606b29216bde8d4ead37df8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-note-more-staff-exits-barret-bob-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mira%20Murati%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20announced%20her%20exit%20from%20the%20company%20Wednesday.%20Now%20two%20others%20are%20also%20leaving%2C%20Sam%20Altman%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Gray)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-note-more-staff-exits-barret-bob-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toiling%20on%20a%20Kenyan%20flower%20farm%20to%20send%20fresh%20roses%20to%20Europe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727311863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F47e3%2Flive%2Fa3a77820-7ba0-11ef-bd5d-77bd3f8a4259.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4glydv8qlgo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20work%20long%20and%20gruelling%20hours%20to%20grow%20the%20flowers%20sold%20across%20Europe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A148%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4glydv8qlgo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4glydv8qlgo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22htt