a.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-1536x1022.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-2048x1363.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367230%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunity%20leaders%20of%20Razai%20Khullen%20village%20are%20felicitated%20for%20their%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20drive%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Ukhrul%2C%20Chingrisoror%20Rumthao%2C%20the%20field%20officer%20with%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20Countering%20Pangolin%20Trafficking%20Project%2C%20recounts%20his%20experiences.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20might%20seem%20completely%20out%20of%20place%20to%20talk%20about%20saving%20wildlife%2C%20when%20hundreds%20of%20people%20are%20getting%20murdered%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20there%20is%20still%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20Chingrisoror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20community%20that%20has%20sustained%20on%20wild%20meat%20for%20generations.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Chingrisoror%20has%20been%20travelling%20from%20village%20to%20village%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20pangolin%20and%20how%20the%20species%20is%20fast%20becoming%20rare%20in%20these%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Tangkhul%20Naga%20himself%2C%20he%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20hunting%20as%20part%20of%20both%20tradition%20and%20sustenance.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20the%20remote%20hills%20have%20little%20access%20to%20modern%20amenities%20and%20livelihoods.%20Medical%20facilities%20are%20limited%20and%20so%20are%20the%20schools.%20There%20are%20still%20villages%20where%20electricity%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20arrived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chingrisoror%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20jobs%20and%20access%20to%20modern%20resources%2C%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20community%20have%20little%20to%20do.%20Hunting%2C%20a%20life%20skill%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20on%20through%20generations%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20both%20productive%20and%20important.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20villages%20like%20Chingjaro%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20buy%20poultry.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20feed%20your%20family%2C%20you%20need%20to%20go%20out%20and%20hunt%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Chingrisoror.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitching%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F92276%2Fwildlife-conservation-trust-tiger-forest-community-development%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTheBetterIndia%2520has%2520partnered%2520with%2520Wildlife%2Clove%2520and%2520association%2520with%2520nature.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20have%20a%20different%20approach%20in%20these%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocally%20known%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ESaaham%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20pangolin%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20diet%20for%20most.%20Its%20scales%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20medicinal%20properties%20and%20this%20alleged%20property%20has%20kept%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20animal%20high%20across%20the%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Manipur%20sharing%20an%20international%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20several%20illegal%20trades%20have%20flourished%20in%20this%20region.%20Alongside%20arms%20and%20drugs%2C%20border%20towns%20like%20Moreh%20have%20been%20the%20hub%20for%20illegal%20wildlife%20smuggling.%20Moreh%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20and%20Namphalong%20on%20the%20Myanmar%20side%20are%20inhabited%20by%20the%20same%20communities.%20This%20makes%20international%20transfers%20easier%20and%20shipments%20of%20pangolins%20and%20pangolin%20scales%20have%20been%20quite%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chinese%20pangolin%20explores%20his%20surrounding%20after%20being%20rescued%20by%20locals%20in%20Ukhrul%2C%20Manipur.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FChinese-pangolin-rescued-by-locals-in-Ukhrul-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Chingrosoror-Rumthao_11zon-1727101591.jpg%201114w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367227%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20Chinese%20pangolin%20explores%20its%20surroundings%20after%20being%20rescued%20by%20locals%20in%20Ukhrul%2C%20Manipur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThomas%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20locals%20would%20load%20trucks%20full%20of%20pangolins%2C%20which%20earned%20them%20good%20money.%E2%80%9D%20Other%20villagers%2C%20who%20wished%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20explained%20that%20the%20business%20has%20worked%20to%20their%20disadvantage.%20The%20locals%20would%20sell%20pangolin%20scales%20at%20rates%20that%20would%20increase%20tenfold%20once%20they%20crossed%20international%20borders.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20pangolin%20has%20become%20rare%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20reasoned%20by%20uninhibited%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20animal%20that%20could%20be%20seen%20almost%20every%20day%20in%20the%20fields%20is%20now%20an%20opportunistic%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20major%20part%20of%20the%20trade%20is%20being%20facilitated%20at%20the%20borders%20where%20refugee%20camps%20are%20in%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20Khavangsing%20Mahakwo%20(name%20changed).%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20locals%20do%20occasionally%20bring%20(or%20used%20to%20bring)%20home%20a%20pangolin%20for%20self-consumption%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20more%20awareness%20in%20these%20camps%2C%20if%20the%20project%20was%20to%20succeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khavangsing%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20for%20people%20trying%20to%20grab%20onto%20any%20resource%20they%20could%20find%2C%20pangolins%20seem%20like%20a%20profitable%20trade-off.%20The%20sacrifice%20of%20wildlife%20for%20a%20few%20extra%20meals%20for%20the%20family%20seems%20justifiable%2C%20even%20if%20the%20law%20says%20otherwise.%20There%20is%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20awareness%2C%20alternatives%2C%20and%20effective%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20mountains%20dry%20up%20without%20the%20pangolins%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20other%20adversities%20attached%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20pangolins%20in%20the%20hills.%20S%20A%20Ramnganing%2C%20former%20President%20of%20the%20Tangkhul%20Naga%20Awunga%20Long%20(TNAL)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20apex%20body%20that%20oversees%20the%20community%20management%20and%20its%20governing%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20decline%20in%20pangolin%20numbers%20has%20made%20the%20hills%20drier.%20It%20is%20an%20animal%20that%20burrows%20and%20opens%20up%20underground%20tunnels%20that%20help%20soak%20up%20rainwater%20and%20keep%20the%20ground%20moist%2C%20all%20around%20the%20year.%20Without%20them%2C%20the%20earth%20dries%20up%2C%20and%20rainwater%20trickles%20down%20to%20the%20valley%2C%20unhindered.%20This%20has%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20whatever%20food%20crops%20we%20try%20to%20grow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20interesting%20insight!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20pangolin%20numbers%20has%20also%20been%20identified%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20increase%20in%20termite%20population%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20just%20more%20termites%20eating%20away%20our%20wooden%20houses%20and%20trees%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramnganing.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20first%20people%20to%20take%20up%20the%20cause%2C%20as%20head%20of%20the%20community%2C%20and%20recently%2C%20the%20TNAL%20took%20a%20historic%20step%20by%20signing%20a%20written%20resolution%20that%20bans%20the%20hunting%20of%20pangolins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202244px)%20100vw%2C%202244px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222244%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20signboard%20in%20Manipur%20addresses%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20pangolins.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549.jpg%202244w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-300x199.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-500x332.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-1536x1021.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-2048x1362.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-1200x798.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignage-to-protect-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727102549-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367233%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221492%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20signboard%20in%20Manipur%20addresses%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20pangolins.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20230%20villages%2C%20including%20Chingjaro%2C%20falling%20under%20the%20apex%20body%2C%20they%20are%20all%20automatic%20signatories%20to%20the%20resolution%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20by%20Chingrisoror%20and%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20already%20spread%20far%20and%20wide.%20The%20pangolin%20(both%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20species)%20is%20protected%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20Schedule%20I%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20(Protection)%20Act%2C%201972.%20However%2C%20The%20TNAL%20resolution%20is%20the%20binding%20law%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20Kashung%20Tennyson%2C%20current%20president%20of%20the%20TNAL%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUntil%20we%20take%20strict%20measures%20in%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20species%2C%20we%20might%20lose%20it%20forever.%20A%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20TNAL%20is%20binding%20for%20all%20members%20of%20the%20community.%20This%20will%20successfully%20disrupt%20the%20existing%20illegal%20trade%20network%20and%20trafficking%20routes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20towards%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20species%20would%20be%20to%20ban%20commercial%20hunting.%20The%20supply%20has%20to%20stop%20if%20we%20are%20to%20save%20pangolins%20in%20India.%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20project%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20WCN%20Pangolin%20Crisis%20Fund%2C%20aims%20to%20raise%20awareness%20alongside%20stricter%20enforcement%20of%20the%20existing%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20support%20to%20the%20cause%2C%20WTI%20has%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20local%20churches%2C%20both%20the%20Baptist%20and%20Catholic.%20At%20the%20Sunday%20gatherings%2C%20the%20pastor%20reads%20out%20from%20a%20pamphlet%20that%20has%20been%20circulated%20among%20the%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESaaham%20madhiman%20khavai%20yangkhami%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20translating%20to%20%E2%80%9CProtect%20the%20Pangolin%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203162px)%20100vw%2C%203162px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223162%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20reads%20a%20brochure%20served%20at%20a%20community%20event%20on%20protecting%20pangolins%20in%20Ngainga%20Village%2C%20Manipur.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607.jpg%203162w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-1536x1022.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-2048x1363.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-on-protecting-pangolins-_-Ngainga-Village-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101607-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367229%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222104%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20man%20reads%20a%20pamphlet%20on%20protecting%20pangolins%20in%20Ngainga%20Village%2C%20Manipur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pamphlet%20starts%20with%20quotes%20like%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20be%20protectors%20of%20GOD%E2%80%99s%20PLAN%20inscribed%20in%20nature%2C%20protectors%20of%20one%20another%20and%20of%20the%20environment%E2%80%9D%20from%20Pope%20Francis%20and%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LORD%20God%20then%20took%20the%20man%20and%20settled%20him%20in%20the%20garden%20of%20Eden%2C%20to%20cultivate%20and%20care%20for%20it%E2%80%9D%20from%20Genesis%202.15.%20The%20message%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20well%20received%20by%20everyone%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIllegal%20wildlife%20trafficking%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%2C%20which%20boasts%20a%20considerable%20population%20of%20the%20Chinese%20pangolin%20(%3Cem%3EManis%20pentadactyla%3C%2Fem%3E)%20has%20been%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20illegal%20international%20markets%20across%20Southeast%20Asia.%20It%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20state%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20pangolin%20seizures%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2665910720300049%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Science%20Direct%20states%20that%2021%25%20of%20pangolin%20seizures%20between%202009%20and%202018%20in%20India%20were%20from%20Manipur%2C%20followed%20by%20Mizoram%20and%20Assam.%20An%20average%20Chinese%20pangolin%20has%20between%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS235198941930424X%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E509%20and%20664%20scales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20combined%20dry%20weight%20of%20about%20467%20grams.%20Imagine%20the%20number%20of%20pangolins%20it%20took%20to%20produce%203%2C248%20kilograms%20of%20pangolin%20scales%20that%20have%20been%20recovered%20in%20Manipur%20alone%2C%20and%20this%20is%20only%20from%20what%20has%20been%20reported%20or%20seized%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20pangolins%20that%20are%20exchanged%20in%20the%20borders.%20Other%20wildlife%2C%20including%20marine%20trophies%20too%20reach%20Manipur%20as%20a%20transit%20to%20the%20international%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jose%20Louies%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20Chief%20of%20Enforcement%20at%20WTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20WTI%20has%20also%20begun%20training%20border%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20forest%20officials%20to%20help%20curb%20the%20trade.%20The%20trainings%20involve%20wildlife%20article%20identification%20and%20understanding%20the%20various%20facets%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20(Protection)%20Act%2C%201972%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20able%20to%20better%20investigate%20a%20case%20and%20achieve%20a%20better%20conviction%20rate%20for%20offenders%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202072px)%20100vw%2C%202072px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-_-angolin-Project-_-Manipur-_-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101599.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20participate%20in%20a%20community%20event%20centred%20around%20the%20protection%20of%20pangolins.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-event-_-angolin-Project-_-Manipur-_-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101599.jpg%202072w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCommunity-even