%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-2-1726842019.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-2-1726842019-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-2-1726842019-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-2-1726842019-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-2-1726842019-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20with%20his%20daughters%20Nandini%20and%20Yachika.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Jaglan%E2%80%99s%20younger%20daughter%20sellotaped%20%E2%80%98period%20rule%E2%80%99%20charts%20in%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20washroom%20at%20her%20school%20when%20she%20discovered%20that%20several%20girls%20never%20knew%20what%20a%20period%20was%3B%20how%20to%20use%20a%20pad%3B%20and%20how%20to%20dispose%20of%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20with%20the%20girls%20by%20his%20side%2C%20Jaglan%20tells%20me%20the%20story%20of%20the%20day%20it%20all%20started.%20%E2%80%9CNandini%20was%20born%20in%202012%20on%20National%20Girl%20Child%20Day.%E2%80%9D%20Initiated%20by%20the%20Government%20in%202008%2C%20the%20day%20was%20earmarked%20for%20spreading%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306628%2Frajasthan-sarpanch-shyam-paliwal-plants-trees-on-birth-of-girl-child-female-foeticide-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawareness%20about%20girl%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20inequalities%20they%20have%20to%20endure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaglan%20recalls%20the%20day%20as%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20the%20nurse%20and%20doctor%20at%20the%20hospital%20begged%20to%20differ.%20%E2%80