ratio.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20832%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%202011.%20Some%20fact-checking%20on%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20through%20the%20years%20tells%20me%20Jaglan%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20surprised%20at%20the%20numbers.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20(in)famous%20for%20having%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20sex%20ratios%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20compounded%20by%20patriarchal%20mindsets%20prevalent%20in%20North%20India%20where%20raising%20a%20girl%20has%20sacrificial%20connotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%202023%20statistics%20point%20out%2C%20that%20mindsets%20are%20seeing%20a%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20916%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Jaglan%20was%20horrified.%20He%20intended%20to%20discuss%20this%20issue%20with%20women%20at%20the%20next%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%20meeting.%20So%2C%20you%20can%20only%20imagine%20his%20surprise%20when%20he%20discovered%20that%20Bibipur%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20a%20male-dominated%20scene.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20women%20had%20to%20pass%20by%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20meeting%20was%20being%20held%2C%20they%20would%20cover%20their%20heads%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghoonghat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20headscarf)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaglan%20shares.%20The%20general%20consensus%20was%20that%20women%20were%20incapable%20of%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349644%2Fcleanest-villages-of-india-mawlynnong-majuli-yana-nako-piplantri-khonoma-chitkul-dawar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage-level%20decisions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20power%20of%20autonomy%20rested%20with%20the%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-ja