dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-4-1726842327-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20spoke%20to%20women%20about%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20female%20foeticide%2C%20dowry%2C%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDadi%20chahegi%20toh%20poti%20aayegi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20young%20brides%20in%20Bibipur%20led%20Jaglan%20to%20discover%20the%20painful%20existence%20they%20had.%20They%20listed%20a%20litany%20of%20atrocities%20ranging%20from%20repeated%20unnecessary%20ultrasounds%20%E2%80%94%20not%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20the%20good%20health%20of%20the%20baby%2C%20but%20instead%20the%20sex%3B%20forced%20abortions%20when%20the%20ultrasound%20revealed%20a%20girl%20foetus%3B%20and%20starvation%20diets%20to%20kill%20the%20girl%20foetus%20when%20aborting%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20issues%20formed%20the%20bedrock%20of%20Jaglan%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENigrani%20Rakhna%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20formula%20was%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20I%20listed%20mothers%20in%20Bibipur%20who%20were%20pregnant%20for%20the%20second%2C%20third%20or%20fourth%20time.%20The%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethen%20assigned%20two%20women%20to%20each%20of%20these%20mothers%20who%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334480%2Ffem-tech-star