The%20only%20thing%20necessary%20for%20the%20triumph%20of%20evil%C2%A0%20is%20for%20good%20men%20to%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20ethical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20directly%20paying%20bribes%2C%20many%20of%20us%20hire%20agents%20or%20brokers%20who%20do%20it%20on%20our%20behalf.%20Anjali%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20go%20out%20of%20your%20way%20to%20bribe.%20If%20you%20break%20a%20traffic%20signal%2C%20pay%20the%20fine%2C%20not%20the%20cop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelp%20those%20in%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20our%20responsibility%20to%20create%20a%20more%20equitable%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20up%20to%20those%20who%20are%20more%20privileged%2C%20focus%20on%20the%20millions%20living%20in%20poverty%20and%20do%20your%20part%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20small%20contribution%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Give%20whatever%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Rs%201%2C000%20or%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20your%20own%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20remain%20modest%20about%20their%20efforts%2C%20the%20Shanmugam%20family%20is%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20for%20us.%20God%20comes%20in%20different%20forms.%20Everyone%20who%20came%20forward%20to%20help%2C%20motivate%2C%20and%20console%20us%2C%20including%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20friends%20and%20juniors%2C%20were%20manifestations%20of%20God.%20They%20showed%20me%20that%20there%20are%20good%20people%20in%20society%2C%20to%20balance%20out%20the%20bad%2C%E2%80%9